{"tid":2341981,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[左膠奶共戲]《神奇女俠1984》特朗普係反派原型","createTime":"2020-12-26T18:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T01:39:50.000Z","uid":249940,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f144344bdec99b4a5c90b22cc95b99d7392c8e64","tid":2341981,"uid":249940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:30:49.000Z","msg":"據外媒報導，DC新片《神奇女俠1984》的服裝設計師Lindy Hemming透露，Pedro Pascal在片中飾演的角色Maxwell Lord ，是從現任美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）獲得了不少啟發。<br />\n<br />\nLindy將Maxwell描述為「一個看起來很有錢，但品味不高的人。」她解釋：<br />\n<br />\n他有可愛的裁縫們給他做非常漂亮的衣服，用了漂亮的布料，非常優雅和昂貴，但是有些東西不太對勁。為什麼？它們不太合身，也不太合適。我相信，當人們看到他的穿搭時，會認為我對做衣服一無所知，但事實是，這正是我們<br />\n<br />\nLindy還補充，<span class=\"red\">他們參考了大量特朗普在80年代的照片：「這和那個年代的特朗普以及商人有些相似。不是嗎？有點俗氣，髮型有點傻乎乎的，以及非常話癆。所以那個角色是現在這個樣子。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static3-cbrimages-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/static3.cbrimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Wonder-Woman-1984-Maxwell-Lord-feature-1.jpg?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;h=500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic3-cbrimages-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fstatic3.cbrimages.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2FWonder-Woman-1984-Maxwell-Lord-feature-1.jpg%3Fq%3D50%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D943%26h%3D500&h=168c2fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">屌 垃圾戲 原來影射Trump</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6581765899e23a6de538e470667e3ba2ba75b055","tid":2341981,"uid":249940,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T18:31:24.000Z","msg":"奶共姬嘉鐸新片《神奇女俠1984》海外票房慘淡 疫情下蝕入肉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2340728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2340728</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"92e7ac47196665e699530a6808130b078da51e1e","tid":2341981,"uid":249940,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,